  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add 1 cup of teff flour to the skillet and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the berbere spice blend, cayenne pepper, and paprika to the skillet and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add 8 oz of Gorgonzola Dolce cheese to the skillet and stir to combine with the spice mixture.",
    "Cook the Gorgonzola mixture for 2-3 minutes, or until it is melted and slightly caramelized.",
    "Stir in the butter until melted.",
    "Season the Gorgonzola mixture with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the Gorgonzola mixture hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro or parsley if desired."
